@startuml
title Precedence Diagram - BitePlate Workflow Dependencies

start
:Login as staff;
:Select role dashboard;

fork
  :Manager monitors dashboard;
fork again
  :Waiter manages tables/reservations;
end fork

:Seat or reserve table;
:Create order;
if (Allergy note?) then (yes)
  :Observer notification sent;
endif
:Add command to kitchen queue;

if (Modify before preparation?) then (yes)
  :Add/remove order item;
else (no)
endif

:Kitchen reprioritise if needed;
:Kitchen process command;
:Order preparing/served;

:Cashier generate bill;
:Choose pricing strategy;
:Apply tax, tip and split bill;
:Singleton OrderHistoryLog records sale;
:Audit log updated;
:Manager reviews report;
stop
@enduml
